    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile engagement through every gear. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a crisp exhaust note. This is a high-performance chassis tuned for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical excellence and analog feedback.",
