      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes an excellent balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint maintains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well, typical of responsible use. The interior is a non-smoker environment, featuring charcoal leather seats that remain firm and supportive with no significant wear or cracking. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule; recent work includes a fresh oil service, new engine air filters, and a coolant flush. The tires have approximately 7/32\" tread remaining, ensuring safety for many miles to come. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, refined cabin experience. Complete service records and two sets of keys are included.",
