      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural weak point. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip these cars are known for. While showing minor signs of use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking a turn-key performance icon.",
